HELLO GRACIE was allowed to settle early, made a four wide move on the turn and came five wide into the lane, gained the place award in the furlong grounds but lost that spot on the wire. UNION FOLLY chased the early pace in between rivals, steadied behind rivals nearing the five sixteenths, then came four wide into the drive and angled out by the furlong marker and had no kick. STORMY SPELL chased the pace four wide, made a three wide bid on the turn, angled in leaving the turn and had no kick. SCHNUER WILL chased the pace on the inside and weakened. COULD BE A COUGAR vied for the lead three wide, then dueled with the winner to her outside and weakened. BOUND BY TRUTH was fractious in the gate, vied for the lead on the inside and faltered.
